            "text_size": "40,15",
            "txt_align": "start",
            "sub_heading": "",
            "heading": "",
            "text": "<p><strong>If you’d like to channel that very elegance and strength this Puja season…</strong> Explore our <strong>Jamdani and Pure Bengal Cotton collection</strong>. Each piece is woven with the spirit of Kolkata and inspired by Rani’s iconic drapes, offering you a chance to wear not just a saree, but a legacy.</p><h2>Sumana Speaks<br/></h2><p>In a nutshell,<strong> </strong>we're endlessly proud of Rani Mukerji for bringing justice, dignity, and poise to a deeply personal story—now immortalized with a National Award. And if you'd like to feel that same grace in your festive wardrobe, our curated Jamdani edit has you lovingly covered.</p><p>Here’s to cinema that celebrates courage—and sarees that remind us why culture matters.</p>",
